&lt;p&gt;Now, beautiful pictures of the garden. &lt;strong&gt;Warning, they may make you want to go check out Kanazawa yourself!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a data-flickr-embed=&#34;true&#34;  href=&#34;https://www.flickr.com/photos/86097314@N03/38319686314/in/album-72157693223773754/&#34; title=&#34;20171113_124015&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4541/38319686314_576306cebb_b.jpg&#34; width=&#34;1024&#34; height=&#34;576&#34; alt=&#34;20171113_124015&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;script async src=&#34;//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js&#34; charset=&#34;utf-8&#34;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a data-flickr-embed=&#34;true&#34;  href=&#34;https://www.flickr.com/photos/86097314@N03/26677759528/in/album-72157693223773754/&#34; title=&#34;IMG_20171114_005814_549&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4753/26677759528_26e6bdb197_b.jpg&#34; width=&#34;1024&#34; height=&#34;576&#34; alt=&#34;IMG_20171114_005814_549&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;script async src=&#34;//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js&#34; charset=&#34;utf-8&#34;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a data-flickr-embed=&#34;true&#34;  href=&#34;https://www.flickr.com/photos/86097314@N03/27259339969/in/album-72157693223773754/&#34; title=&#34;20171113_130657&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4557/27259339969_a4c3a206ae_b.jpg&#34; width=&#34;576&#34; height=&#34;1024&#34; alt=&#34;20171113_130657&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;script async src=&#34;//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js&#34; charset=&#34;utf-8&#34;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a data-flickr-embed=&#34;true&#34;  href=&#34;https://www.flickr.com/photos/86097314@N03/27259343949/in/album-72157693223773754/&#34; title=&#34;20171113_131149&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4586/27259343949_1025a15066_b.jpg&#34; width=&#34;1024&#34; height=&#34;576&#34; alt=&#34;20171113_131149&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;script async src=&#34;//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js&#34; charset=&#34;utf-8&#34;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
Amidst the garden I saw a little gardenhouse (Seisonkaku Villa) and decided to take the tour. This doll apparently survived the great burning of Kanazawa and is therefore haunted.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a data-flickr-embed=&#34;true&#34;  href=&#34;https://www.flickr.com/photos/86097314@N03/25164746448/in/album-72157693223773754/&#34; title=&#34;20171113_131557&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4601/25164746448_48204646b7_b.jpg&#34; width=&#34;1024&#34; height=&#34;576&#34; alt=&#34;20171113_131557&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;script async src=&#34;//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js&#34; charset=&#34;utf-8&#34;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a data-flickr-embed=&#34;true&#34;  href=&#34;https://www.flickr.com/photos/86097314@N03/38319769004/in/album-72157693223773754/&#34; title=&#34;20171113_133657&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4599/38319769004_8b3320e5d1_b.jpg&#34; width=&#34;576&#34; height=&#34;1024&#34; alt=&#34;20171113_133657&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;script async src=&#34;//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js&#34; charset=&#34;utf-8&#34;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
I loved these girls&amp;rsquo;s kimono.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a data-flickr-embed=&#34;true&#34;  href=&#34;https://www.flickr.com/photos/86097314@N03/39035744071/in/album-72157693223773754/&#34; title=&#34;20171113_134311&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4736/39035744071_d2e7ce6f9e_b.jpg&#34; width=&#34;576&#34; height=&#34;1024&#34; alt=&#34;20171113_134311&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;script async src=&#34;//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js&#34; charset=&#34;utf-8&#34;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

